#
# Handle different arrow-key key-sequences when in a terminal emulator
# http://stackoverflow.com/questions/4548106/screen-somehow-unmaps-my-arrow-keys-in-emacs-after-a-z
#
# To install the changes, run "lesskey"
# http://linux.die.net/man/1/lesskey
#
#command
\eOA   back-line-force
\e[A   back-line-force
\eOB   forw-line-force
\e[B   forw-line-force
\eOC   right-scroll
\e[C   right-scroll
\eOD   left-scroll
\e[D   left-scroll
